name: Panel Gag
description:
For when you need someone to be very quiet and they tend to be bratty and push a normal gag out.

Keep weights under one.

Will occasionally produce horrors beyond human comprehension.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
Consider this a first draft - Tends to like putting a big collar on (but I'm here for it), and clothing tends to get rather... strappy.

Sometimes likes to put the faces straps on, other times just one or weirdly, sometimes not at all!
